01:36:24,960 --> 01:36:27,129
Aku tahu, Bella, bernapaslah.

1015
01:36:33,511 --> 01:36:34,595
Alice!

1016
01:36:34,678 --> 01:36:36,472
Bella, dia tak bisa
membaca pikiranmu.

1017
01:36:36,555 --> 01:36:39,642
Jika aku pergi, dia pikir aku
berbohong. Dia akan bergegas.

1018
01:36:40,726 --> 01:36:43,270
- Lewat mana?
